title: Me in 10 seconds
text:
Timeline for context
2014: Marketing + Sales funnel analytics for Microsoft Lumia campaigns in India.
2016: Freelance Data Analytics + Visualisation for Print + Social Media agencies.

Medium-scale businesses with a focus on creating more re-usable IP
Scaled to mid-5-figure revenue
Shut down in mid-2017 owing to health complications and burnout

2017: Data Science consultant @ Deloitte US-India

12 countries, 3M$+ impact

2020: Moved to Germany - to research NLP & Speech
